FuncDef:
The isis ppp-osicp-check command enables OSICP check on a PPP interface.
The undo isis ppp-osicp-check command cancels the setting. The isis ppp-osicp-check command enables OSICP check on a PPP interface. The undo isis ppp-osicp-check command cancels the setting. By default, IS-IS ignores checking OSICP.
